# Copy 呢個檔做 .env.local（next dev）同／或 .dev.vars（wrangler / opennextjs-cloudflare），再填真值。
#
# 最少要 set：VENICE_API_KEY — 唔係嘅話 /api/scan 會報錯，個 app 核心功能唔會郁。
# 其餘全部可選（Turnstile、Stripe、admin）。
#
# Turnstile（可選）：https://developers.cloudflare.com/turnstile/ — 幫免費 scan 擋 bot

# --- Venice AI（必填；SEO scan）---
VENICE_API_KEY=
# Optional; default: venice-uncensored
# VENICE_MODEL=venice-uncensored
# Optional; default: 3
# FREE_DAILY_SCANS=3

# --- Cloudflare Turnstile (optional; if unset, scan API does not require a challenge) ---
# NEXT_PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=
# TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY=

# --- Stripe (optional; needed for Subscribe / checkout / webhooks) ---
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
# STRIPE_PRICE_ID=
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
# Optional origin for checkout redirects; falls back to request Origin or site URL
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://your-domain.com

# --- Admin (optional; /api/admin/benchmark) ---
# CRAWLME_ADMIN_SECRET=
